Arsenal Agrees to Sign German Defender Per Mertesacker from Werder Bremen

-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 
2011-08-31T15:12:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/arsenal-agrees-to-sign-german-defender-per-mertesacker-from-werder-bremen.html
Arsenal said it agreed to bring in
Werder Bremen’s Per Mertesacker, the second defender the north
London soccer club signed today.  The 26-year-old member of the German national team has
played for eight years in  Germany ’s top league. Arsenal
announced the signing in a statement today on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
